data.description: If you are looking for  a lot of living space for a great price, then this is your new home. Unique floor plan for a duplex with a 1st floor bedroom with a roll in shower, family room, laundry and large eat-in kitchen and living room.  the 2nd floor has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. the lower level is finished with 2 more rooms. this a lot of house for the money. There is a deck that goes across the whole width of the house. Great  location for the MD commuter. Make your appointment to see today! Home is being sold in "as is " condition.
